<function>

access:  static public

name: exception

param: string, $class

param: mixed, $code

param: string, $text, ''

param: array, $info, array ()

return: object

</function>

Generates a simple exception, but does not throw it.

* Parameters:

 * string //$class//: The class that generated the exception.

 * mixed //$code//: A scalar error code, generally a string.

 * string //$text//: Any error message text.

 * array //$info//: Additional error information in an associative array.

* Returns object: A Solar_Exception object.